title: Aruba Networks Wireless LAN Controller (WLC): Number of Wifi connections
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/aruba
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This checks display the amount of connected clients in an wireless network.
 Per default the check only displays the information for each network, and also one
 summary. Levels can be set for each network via WATO.

item:
 Name of the wifi or "Summary" for the overall number of clients.

inventory:
 One service is created for each wifi network and one summary service is created.
